   3.2.2 Operation of Routers (2/2) 
     n   Routing   mechanism  : the action of looking     an address up in a table and deciding
 what     to do with the IP
 datagram -&gt; Performed by     IP     n   Routing   policy  : the actual algorithms that     are use to make routing calculations and
 fill     the routing table
 with forwarding entries -&gt;     Performed
